OL,3,CLandlady threatens 'legal action'
OL,4,Cafter pub hit by flooding four times
OL,6,FThe landlady of a pub in
OL,7,FLeicestershire says recent flooding
OL,8,Fmeans she has been forced to close her
OL,9,Fdoors again - despite already spending
OL,10,Faround thirty thousand pounds on
OL,11,Frepairs.
OL,13,FJo Towle, who runs the Crown and
OL,14,FPlough in Long Clawson, has been
OL,15,Fflooded four times in the past five
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
