OL,3,CLandlady threatens 'legal action'
OL,4,Cafter pub hit by flooding four times
OL,6,FJo, who has been the local landlady
OL,7,Ffor thirty years, says she is now
OL,8,Fseeking legal advice on how to
OL,9,Fapproach the County Council and the
OL,10,FBorough Council, alleging they have
OL,11,Fdisplayed a 'lack of action' following
OL,12,Fthe floods.
OL,14,F"So in 2019 we flooded in November,
OL,15,Ffive months later we flooded again in
OL,16,FFebruary 2020", explains Jo. "In march
OL,17,Fwe were forced into lockdown and then
OL,18,Fwe flooded again last January in 2024
OL,19,Fand this January in 2025".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
