OL,3,CLandlady threatens 'legal action'
OL,4,Cafter pub hit by flooding four times
OL,6,F"We've had a really tough five years
OL,7,Fjust trying to keep afloat", she adds.
OL,9,FJo suggests that there has not been
OL,10,Fenough effort from Leicestershire
OL,11,FCounty Council and Melton Borough
OL,12,FCouncil to keep drains clear during
OL,13,Fthe floods, which has contributed to
OL,14,Fthe impact it has had on locals and
OL,15,Fbusinesses in the area.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
