OL,3,CLandlady threatens 'legal action'
OL,4,Cafter pub hit by flooding four times
OL,6,FThe landlady lives at the pub with her
OL,7,Fhusband but she says it's pointless
OL,8,Fpaying to replace their equipment and
OL,9,Fopen the business again until the
OL,10,Fculvert in the village is completely
OL,11,Fcleared out.
OL,13,FThe structure has multiple owners and
OL,14,FJo says it makes it difficult to know
OL,15,Fwho is responsible for the blockage.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
