OL,6,F"I've been having to find surveys and
OL,7,Fhistory and who owns what and things",
OL,8,Fsays Jo. "So now I'm just going to
OL,9,Fhave to take legal action, that's what
OL,10,Fwe're looking at, just getting some
OL,11,Flegal advice at the moment".
OL,13,FLeicestershire County Council said:
OL,14,F"We fully understand the significant
OL,15,Fconcerns of residents and businesses
OL,16,Fimpacted by flooding across
OL,17,FLeicestershire.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
