OL,6,F"January's rainfalls saw record river
OL,7,Flevels which saw more than 800 homes
OL,8,Fand businesses flooded. We are seeing
OL,9,Fmore frequent instances due to climate
OL,10,Fchange, and we have written the
OL,11,Fgovernment urging them to give us
OL,12,Fsupport for long-term flooding
OL,13,Fsolutions across the county.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
