OL,3,CLandlady threatens 'legal action'
OL,4,Cafter pub hit by flooding four times
OL,6,F"We are looking to invest #1m of
OL,7,Fadditional council funds to support
OL,8,Fmore investigations and extra cash to
OL,9,Fclear drains of flood debris and fix
OL,10,Fimmediate damage, taking total
OL,11,Finvestment on flood and drainage works
OL,12,Fto more than #18m over the next four
OL,13,Fyears."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
