OL,3,CLandlady threatens 'legal action'
OL,4,Cafter pub hit by flooding four times
OL,6,F"The culvert in Long Clawson has
OL,7,Fmultiple responsible owners. The last
OL,8,Fsurvey showed that the county council-
OL,9,Fmaintained areas were clear, and we
OL,10,Fhave been in liaison consistently with
OL,11,Fthe other owners of the culvert to
OL,12,Fmake them aware of their
OL,13,Fresponsibilities."
OL,15,FMeanwhile, Melton Borough Council told
OL,16,FITV News Central that it appreciates
OL,17,Fthe importance of the Crown and Plough
OL,18,FPub to the community and the residents
OL,19,Fof Long Clawson. It also added that it
OL,20,Funderstands the "devastating impact"
OL,21,Fthat flooding can have on communities.
