OL,6,F"As such, we are continuing to work
OL,7,Fwith our partners across the county to
OL,8,Funderstand issues that arise and
OL,9,Fsupport our communities that have been
OL,10,Fimpacted. Together, we have been
OL,11,Flobbying the government to release
OL,12,Fmore grant funding to support our
OL,13,Fcommunities in Leicestershire. Our
OL,14,Fpartners have also liaised with the
OL,15,FEnvironment Agency (EA) regarding
OL,16,Fopportunities for The Crown and Plough
OL,17,Fpub to be included in available flood
OL,18,Fresilience schemes."
